{"id": "ChIJI4JGZTh_hYARnbxxtSghhBc", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 44, "displayName": {"text": "Sizzling Lunch Berkeley", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJI4JGZTh_hYARnbxxtSghhBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205V2FHZDROM3BhTmtFNVgwRXRlRlJ2VmpOdFRGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "whenever I come to the Bay Area, I always want to eat here!! the portions are large, warm and super yummy. I like to add kimchi and the 2 sauces that are provided at the table. I can't believe there are only 40 something reviews for this restaurant! it is a gem in my opinion. and the guy who works there is the goat! 🥰", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "whenever I come to the Bay Area, I always want to eat here!! the portions are large, warm and super yummy. I like to add kimchi and the 2 sauces that are provided at the table. I can't believe there are only 40 something reviews for this restaurant! it is a gem in my opinion. and the guy who works there is the goat! 🥰", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "desiree", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106587503673721940284/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZc2TIyyYpbVWVNrLrriL76RxxSXO5GlLC90NAULGoWZZxjxUo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-03T01:15:32.875616707Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205V2FHZDROM3BhTmtFNVgwRXRlRlJ2VmpOdFRGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205V2FHZDROM3BhTmtFNVgwRXRlRlJ2VmpOdFRGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f3865468223:0x17842128b571bc9d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJI4JGZTh_hYARnbxxtSghhBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WeE1Xa3hjMFkwVWtab1ZYbzBVRWx4ZDFKTVpsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "I wanted a quick meal, so I ordered the Onion Beef Pepper Rice, which came with Green onions, corn, garlic butter, salt, pepper, and Fried Crispy Onion. The portion size was great, but the flavors felt a bit mild for me. I ended up adding the garlic shoyu and teriyaki sauces, though I could mostly taste the sweetness and saltiness. Overall, it was a mixed experience. But I'll definitely come back to try it again another time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I wanted a quick meal, so I ordered the Onion Beef Pepper Rice, which came with Green onions, corn, garlic butter, salt, pepper, and Fried Crispy Onion. The portion size was great, but the flavors felt a bit mild for me. I ended up adding the garlic shoyu and teriyaki sauces, though I could mostly taste the sweetness and saltiness. Overall, it was a mixed experience. But I'll definitely come back to try it again another time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alice Hou", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118209491174900771446/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDlKWFVtHXfi5RlpYkOa9AJ3kzi4zvRKi2-61rc7TPsbKteJB7RQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-31T19:44:06.664452076Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WeE1Xa3hjMFkwVWtab1ZYbzBVRWx4ZDFKTVpsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WeE1Xa3hjMFkwVWtab1ZYbzBVRWx4ZDFKTVpsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f3865468223:0x17842128b571bc9d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJI4JGZTh_hYARnbxxtSghhBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SNGQxVkZVRjlRYjNaWk0yeGtlVlpzTUhOQ0xVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "I ain't entering my phone and email just to order food are u kidding me dawg\n\nthe man working there was very polite and informed me that unfortunately there was no way to bypass this except for entering a fake phone number and email.  He did a great job, whoever is the owner here needs to get their stuff together and realize no one's tryna go through all that just to get a curry.  I'm 29 and don't wanna deal with all that, how do you think my grandparents are gonna feel when you tell them the menu is a QR code and the servers have no way of taking your order directly?", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I ain't entering my phone and email just to order food are u kidding me dawg\n\nthe man working there was very polite and informed me that unfortunately there was no way to bypass this except for entering a fake phone number and email.  He did a great job, whoever is the owner here needs to get their stuff together and realize no one's tryna go through all that just to get a curry.  I'm 29 and don't wanna deal with all that, how do you think my grandparents are gonna feel when you tell them the menu is a QR code and the servers have no way of taking your order directly?", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alori", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111914627907043995967/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpLkO6xfDF4OwsnR1-U90-c-q9M0M4oENXbu_QO93URA0r6iN3=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-19T22:55:48.746754898Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SNGQxVkZVRjlRYjNaWk0yeGtlVlpzTUhOQ0xVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SNGQxVkZVRjlRYjNaWk0yeGtlVlpzTUhOQ0xVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f3865468223:0x17842128b571bc9d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJI4JGZTh_hYARnbxxtSghhBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJMllYWnBaMGhFY2pKeFIyaHFOM2QwWWw4elIyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I’ve enjoyed coming to Sizzling Lunch my entire time in college. It’s a fun experience and I enjoy the food as well. I find the prices to be steep and constantly increasing for food that isn’t actually cooked by anyone", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’ve enjoyed coming to Sizzling Lunch my entire time in college. It’s a fun experience and I enjoy the food as well. I find the prices to be steep and constantly increasing for food that isn’t actually cooked by anyone", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Steph L.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103751142715987862550/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtBt2jvxJZ4Bk9ZZ57XvauWhxwnQQ8z6kR_7eYjxSz_QzaAbg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-01T03:12:29.262995866Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJMllYWnBaMGhFY2pKeFIyaHFOM2QwWWw4elIyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJMllYWnBaMGhFY2pKeFIyaHFOM2QwWWw4elIyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f3865468223:0x17842128b571bc9d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJI4JGZTh_hYARnbxxtSghhBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Cc2RFdFBWamgyTkRsR1NIbDJTV0pNWjFoSWRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had the beef curry with rice, cheese and added mushrooms on the hot plate. Had the house salad on the side as well.Food came out very quick. Love the sizzling plates. Really hit the spot! We will be back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had the beef curry with rice, cheese and added mushrooms on the hot plate. Had the house salad on the side as well.Food came out very quick. Love the sizzling plates. Really hit the spot! We will be back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Emmanuel Dinardi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105597279526734705866/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIp0oFO2Vt_QEi4JGn1BgviIrVT